data.name: StringTable.WarningText
data.value:
To avoid injury from unintended vehicle movement, perform the following:
    - Park the vehicle on a level surface.
    - Chock the tires.
    - Remain in the driver’s seat and keep the brake pressed.
    - Be ready to stop the procedure if necessary.
